==References==
*This item refers to [[Wikipedia:Gary Gygax|Gary Gygax]], credited with the co-creation of [[Wikipedia:Dungeons & Dragons|Dungeons & Dragons]]
*A "libram" is a type of spellbook in the contexts of many RPGs.  It is not a standard English word.  While first found in Vance's [[wikipedia:The Dying Earth|The Dying Earth]], Gary Gygax's use of it in D&D is [http://phrontistery.info/disq6.html responsible] for its ubiquity in the fantasy genre.

